	<div class="row">
	
		<div class="grid_8">
        	<div class="header" style="margin-top:5px;">
				<h2><em>2016 Ontario Budget</em>: Jobs for Today and Tomorrow</h2>
        	</div>
			<div class="content">
			  
			  <p>People from all corners of the world choose Ontario, knowing it is a great place to live, work and raise a family. We have a strong, diversified economy that is creating good jobs and will provide retirement security. Our current strong economic performance shows that our plan is working. We will continue to focus on our number-one priority â creating economic growth and more jobs. </p>
			  <p>The people of Ontario are looking past economic cycles, election cycles, and even life cycles to do what is right for our children and grandchildren. These are not easy choices but they are the right ones â an economic plan that is creating jobs for today and tomorrow. </p>
			  <p>The <em>2016 Ontario Budget</em> is building on the  government&rsquo;s plan to grow the economy, create jobs and balance the budget by  2017â18. </p>
			  <p><strong><a href="budget/ontariobudgets/2016/index.html">Read the 2016 Ontario Budget</a></strong></p>
              <p><strong><a href="http://news.ontario.ca/mof/en/2016/02/ontarios-investments-creating-jobs-for-today-and-tomorrow.html">Read the News Release</a></strong></p>
              <p><a href="budget/ontariobudgets/2016/budhi.html">Read the Highlights</a></p>
	      </div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="grid_4">
			<div class="header" style="margin-top: 5px;">
				<h2>Personal Income Tax</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="content" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
				<p>The <a class="external" href="http://www.cra-arc.gc.ca/tx/ndvdls/menu-eng.html">Canada Revenue Agency (CRA)</a> administers personal income tax and the <acronym title="Harmonized Sales Tax">HST</acronym> on behalf of Ontario and can answer your questions by <a class="external" href="http://www.cra-arc.gc.ca/cntct/phn-eng.html">telephone</a>.</p>
			</div>
		
			<div class="header">
				<h2><abbr title="Ontario's Tax Services">ONT-TAXS</abbr> online</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="content" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
				<div class="initiatives">
					<p><a href="/en/services/onttaxs/index.html">About <abbr title="Ontario's Tax Services">ONT-TAXS</abbr> online</a></p>
					<p><a href="/en/services/onttaxs/cif.html">Get Started</a></p>
					<p><a href="https://www.iaa.gov.on.ca/iaalogin/IAALogin.jsp">Login to ON<em>e-key</em></a></p>
					<p class="last"><a href="/en/services/index.html">Other Online Services</a></p>
				</div>
			</div>
            
           <div class="header" style="margin-top: 5px;">
				<h2>Ontario Interactive Digital Media Tax Credit</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="content" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
				<p>Read about the proposed changes to the Ontario Interactive Digital Media Tax Credit. Read the <a href="/en/credit/oidmtc/bulletin-may-6-2015.html">May 6, 2015 Bulletin</a>.</p>
			</div> 
			
	  </div>
	</div>    
    
	<div class="row" style="margin-top:-25px;">
		<p style="margin-bottom:10px;"><a href="/en/taxcredits/index.html?utm_source=finance&utm_medium=homebanner&utm_campaign=homepromo"><img src="/en/taxcredits/images/calculator.gif" alt="Tax Credit Calculator. Are you getting money back?" /></a></p>
	</div>

	<div class="row">

		<div class="grid_6">
		  	<div class="header">
				<h2><a href="/en/reformcommission/">Public Sector Salary Disclosure</a></h2>
			</div>
          <div class="content">
            
 				<p>View the annual list of public sector employees who were paid a salary of $100,000 or more.</p>
				<p><a href="http://www.ontario.ca/salarydisclosure">2016 Salary Disclosure (Disclosure for 2015)</a></p>
				<p><a href="https://www.ontario.ca/page/public-sector-salary-disclosure-act-disclosures-2014">2015 Salary Disclosure (Disclosure for 2014)</a></p>
                <p><a href="/en/publications/salarydisclosure/pssd/">Previous Disclosures</a></p>
          </div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="grid_6">
			<div class="header">
				<h2>Ontario Retirement Pension Plan </h2>
			
		  </div>
			<div class="content">
				<p>The Ontario Retirement Pension Plan (ORPP): A made-in-Ontario  pension solution to help Ontario workers retire with greater financial security.</p>
				<p><a href="https://www.ontario.ca/page/orpp-ontario-retirement-pension-plan">Read more about the ORPP</a>.</p>
		  </div>
		</div>
	
	</div>
	
